"финансовыми инструментами."
msgstr ""
"The information on this website is for reference and informational purposes "
"only. It is not a public offer, an invitation to invest, or an invitation to "
"enter into transactions with securities or other financial instruments."

#: templates/core/disclaimers.html:30
msgid "Ключевые положения:"
msgstr "Key provisions:"

#: templates/core/disclaimers.html:32
msgid ""
